== 人口 ==
根據萊斯布里奇市政府於2011年進行的市內人口普查，萊市共有87,882名居民<ref name="census">{{cite web |title=2011 census results - City of Lethbridge is home to 1,223 new residents |publisher=City of Lethbridge |url=http://www.lethbridge.ca/NewsCentre/Pages/official-census-results-2011.aspx |accessdate=2011-06-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110815135839/http://www.lethbridge.ca/NewsCentre/Pages/official-census-results-2011.aspx |archivedate=2011-08-15 }}</ref>，較2010年市內人口普查所得的86,659人上升1.4%<ref name=2010pop>{{cite web | url=http://www.municipalaffairs.alberta.ca/documents/msb/2010pop.pdf | title=2010 Official Population List | publisher=Alberta Municipal Affairs | date=2010-09-15 | accessdate=2011-06-22 | archive-date=2011-07-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110706164319/http://www.municipalaffairs.alberta.ca/documents/msb/2010pop.pdf | dead-url=no }}</ref>。據2006年加拿大全國人口普查，萊市有74,637名居民，都會區人口則為95,196<ref name=statcan2006>[http://www12.statcan.ca/english/census06/data/profiles/community/Details/Page.cfm?Lang=E&Geo1=CSD&Code1=4802012&Geo2=PR&Code2=48&Data=Count&SearchText=Lethbridge&SearchType=Begins&SearchPR=01&B1=All Lethbridge Community Profile] {{Wayback|url=http://www12.statcan.ca/english/census06/data/profiles/community/Details/Page.cfm?Lang=E&Geo1=CSD&Code1=4802012&Geo2=PR&Code2=48&Data=Count&SearchText=Lethbridge&SearchType=Begins&SearchPR=01&B1=All |date=20080422074558 }} Statistics Canada. 2007. 2006 Community Profiles. Released March 13, 2007. Last modified: 2007-03-13.</ref>。萊市人口以白人為主；2006年每8個萊市居民中有1人並非歐裔<ref name=statcan2006/>，而2001年每10人中則有1人為非歐裔<ref name="stats">[http://www12.statcan.ca/english/Profil01/CP01/Details/Page.cfm?Lang=E&Geo1=CSD&Code1=4802012&Geo2=PR&Code2=48&Data=Count&SearchText=lethbridge&SearchType=Begins&SearchPR=01&B1=All&Custom= Lethbridge Community Profile] {{Wayback|url=http://www12.statcan.ca/english/Profil01/CP01/Details/Page.cfm?Lang=E&Geo1=CSD&Code1=4802012&Geo2=PR&Code2=48&Data=Count&SearchText=lethbridge&SearchType=Begins&SearchPR=01&B1=All&Custom= |date=20071217060434 }} Statistics Canada. 2002. 2001 Community Profiles. Released June 27, 2002. Last modified: 2006-12-14. Statistics Canada Catalogue no. 93F0053XIE</ref>。非歐裔居民中有40%為[[加拿大原住民|加拿大原住民]]；其他族裔則包括日裔、華裔和拉美裔。

2006年全國人口普查亦顯示萊市居民為母語比例以英文（超過85%）為首，其次為德文（約4%）、荷蘭文（約2%）、法文（約1%）、中文（約1%）和西班牙文（約1%）<ref>{{cite web | title = Lethbridge | work =  Detailed Mother Tongue (186), Knowledge of Official Languages (5), Age Groups (17A) and Sex (3) for the Population of Canada, Provinces, Territories, Census Metropolitan Areas and Census Agglomerations, 2001 and 2006 Censuses - 20% Sample Data | publisher = Statistics Canada | date = 20 November 2007 | url = http://www12.statcan.ca/english/census06/data/topics/RetrieveProductTable.cfm?ALEVEL=3&APATH=3&CATNO=&DETAIL=0&DIM=&DS=99&FL=0&FREE=0&GAL=0&GC=99&GK=NA&GRP=1&IPS=&METH=0&ORDER=1&PID=89201&PTYPE=88971&RL=0&S=1&ShowAll=No&StartRow=1&SUB=701&Temporal=2006&Theme=70&VID=0&VNAMEE=&VNAMEF=&GID=838048 | accessdate = 2008-02-06}}</ref>。

